<A>__{the man walking aimlessly.}
<L>__{exterior zurich park night}
<A>__{the man trying to get comfortable on a bench. it's chilly but this will have to do until morning. just settling in, when }
<P>__{zurich cop #1 (o.s.) (authority german)}
<D>__{can't you read the signs?}
<A>__{the man turns. two zurich cops coming toward him.}
<D>__{zurich cop #2 on your feet. let's go. right now.}
<A>__{the man makes his feet. they're on top of him now.}
<D>__{zurich cop #1 the park is closed. there's no sleeping in the park. zurich cop #2 let's see some identification.}
<A>__{the man not sure what to do. eyes moving. mouth shut.}
<D>__{zurich cop #1 come on. your papers. let's go.}
